>> VM Management Problem:

1. OS Installation
2. Time consuming
3. Manual -- human error
4. Tough to replicate multi vms
5. Need to document entire setup

>> Vagrant for VMs 
1. No OS Installation  
    - VM Images/Box
    - Free box avialable on Vagrant cloud
2. Vagrant file
    - Manage all vm settings in a file
    - VM changes through Vaagrantfile
    - Easy Provisioning


>> Step by Step to create a vm using vagrant

- vagrant init <image-name>     ## image name is available vagrant cloud site
- vagrant up
- vagrant ssh
- vagrant halt
- vagrant global-status
- vagrant global-status prune
- vagrant destroy

